{
  "stem": "3658.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 18.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was the scout, obviously.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they saw, they knew that the Americans are there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They can't do anything, or he can-- you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It wouldn't look good if they killed him and the rest came with him.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, well, I suppose he didn't know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But that's what I remember.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, other Jeeps might have been behind.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I can only remember the one Jeep driving in that we saw.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we lifted each other up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we held each other.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then we started to, you know, to say, we are free.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And people started to cry, you know?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then we started to get out of the camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we couldn't walk by ourselves.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we held each other.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And of course, the Americans were very, very kind and very good.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They start throwing chocolates [SOBBING] and food.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we started to eat like crazy because you know, we were so starving, so hungry.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And of course, that's when a lot of people got sick and died like flies on the road.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We went out on the main highway.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we just picked up everything they were throwing from the trucks.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They could see the who we are.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we were very, very sick, all of us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the first night, I remember, went up on a little, a little hill.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was a house.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we sat down.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The Germans, nobody was there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We sat outside.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We made a fire.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the few that could still walk, and we sang [NON-ENGLISH], you know?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I still remember that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then we went in to Wels, a place called Wels.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That's the town next to Gunskirchen, was Wels, in Austria, which must not have been very far from there.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
